original: Källoff, Nils, e. o. hovrätts fiskal, Jönköping, f. 29/7/12 i Sthlm av stads-kamr. Ossian K. o. Annie Hultgren. G. 36 m. Iduna Malmström. Barn: Margareta f. 38. — Stud:ex. i Jönköp. 31, jur. kand. i Lund 36. Tingstjg. i Vili-andisi diomis. 36-3(9, e. o. not. i Göta hovr. 39-40, fiskal där 40, tingssekr. i Sunnervikens dom«. 42-46, e. o. fiskal i Göta hovr. 46, adj. led. s. å. Hobby: sv. frimärken.
translated: Källoff, Nils, temporary associate judge's fiscal, Jönköping, born on July 29, 1912 in Stockholm to city commissioner Ossian K. and Annie Hultgren. Married in 1936 to Iduna Malmström. Children: Margareta born in 1938. Completed high school in Jönköping in 1931, obtained a law degree in Lund in 1936. Served as a judicial assistant in Vili-andisi diomis from 1936-1939, temporary notary at Göta Court of Appeal in 1939-1940, fiscal there from 1940, court clerk at Sunnerviken district court from 1942-1946, temporary fiscal at Göta Court of Appeal in 1946, adjunct member in the same year. Hobby: Swedish stamps.
